bors r+

@fpvandoorn Let's go with S being an implementation detail for now. I don't want anyone making use of the internal encoding. Plus, I don't have time to develop theory about S and S.encode, or to brainstorm names.

Maybe we'll reconsider in a followup PR where it handles indexed types. I had some code somewhere with some experiments with a scheme for this, but it's been a few months and I'm not sure where it's gone.

